Package: RcppThrust
Type: Package
Title: RcppThrust: Parallel R with Thrust and Rcpp
Version: 0.1-0
Description: Thrust is a powerful tool for parallel programming. This package
    demonstrates how to use Thrust in a package that otherwise integrates C++
    code using Rcpp. This package is based on Rth by Norm Matloff and Drew
    Schmidt.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Depends: Rcpp
SystemRequirements: GNU make. Nvidia's CUDA toolkit (>= release 8.0).
Author: Jan Tilly
Maintainer: Jan Tilly <jantilly@gmail.com>
Suggests: testthat
